name: Yogi FineCare
overview:
Established in the year 2012, we, “Yogi Fine Care” are a recognized organizations, engaged in manufacturing, supplying and distributing a commendable assortment of Protein Granule, Energy Drink, Antioxidant Capsule and Iron & Zinc Syrup.

Products: Our offered range encompasses of Yogivita, Sugar Free Yafargin Granule, Stamina-CZ and Yogilyte-CZ. In addition to this, we also offer YLOPIC-M Capsule, YBETA-S Capsule, YOGIRON-CZ Capsule, YLOPIN-L Capsule and A-Red Syrup.

Our Team: Backed by a highly talented and competent team of professionals, we are able to manufacture our entire range of Protein Granule, Energy Drink, Antioxidant Capsule and Iron & Zinc Syrup with utmost perfection.

Our Quality: Quality being a prime concern for our organization, hence, we pay immense attention while manufacturing our range of Protein Granule, Energy Drink, Antioxidant Capsule and Iron & Zinc Syrup.

Our Infrastructure: To keep in sync with the latest market trends, we have developed a sophisticated infrastructure facility at our premises, which is sprawls across an extensive area of 1440 square feet. Our infrastructure enable us in processing our range of Protein Granule, Energy Drink, Antioxidant Capsule and Iron & Zinc Syrup with efficiency.

Client Satisfaction: Being a client-centric organization, we follow client oriented approaches in processing our range of Protein Granule, Energy Drink, Antioxidant Capsule and Iron & Zinc Syrup.
